title: About
text:
Featuring posts by RCS staff on data science, research computing, and related tools and methods.
We share practical guidance, technical insights, and explorations of emerging ideas that support and inspire the HBS research community. Topics range from hands-on tutorials to reflections on workflows, reproducibility, and research best practices.
